snippet: Nascar will have a new champion as the Chase for the Sprint Cup championship will go on without Brad Keselowski, the reigning champion.
abstract: Brad Keselowski, reigning Nascar champion, fails to make the 12-driver Chase for the Sprint Cup at Richmond International Raceway in Virginia.
lead_paragraph: Nascar will have a new champion as the Chase for the Sprint Cup championship will go on without Brad Keselowski, the reigning champion.
